        <Parent_String>modern North American architecture styles and movements [300018197], modern North American [300018196], modern American [300018115], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
